Twenty one, twenty two--

[dropping ears in basket]

Adoption? You can't adopt a gobbo! That would be like adopting a bear or a boar! Sure they are find when they are a cub or a piglet but when they grow up they go wild and attack!

--------

Twenty five, twenty six. Twenty six ears! That's twenty six gold you owe us Mister King's Cashier!

Don't say I didn't warn you.

--------

